      <title>Implicit type conversion in GDScript - When math gets in the way</title>
      <link>https://davcri.github.io/posts/gdscript-implicit-type-conversion/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Nov 2018 12:00:59 +0000</pubDate>
